attributes.label: The said bank account has not been operated by me/us for a long time. I/we understand that as per policy, the bank has classified the said account as "Dormant". I/we now agree to operate the said bank account regularly and request you to re- classify the account as "Active". I/we also undertake to make transaction(s) on the same day my account is activated from dormancy.l/we confirm having received my/our statement for the period of dormancy at the time of placing this request.
